  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6556160/" class="title-link">语境的语境</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6556160"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Eversint/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2790683-34.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Eversint/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Ubique</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-02-20"
      class="main-meta">2014-02-20 20:53:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6556160_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  （一） 众所周知，在简化的意义上，可以把波考克、斯金纳、邓恩为代表的剑桥学派，称作“语境主义”。他们的政治思想史（或政治话语史）理路非常强调对文献诞生时的话语环境与话语的历史脉络的考察。这势必一方面要求历史学家掌握语言学乃至语言哲学的方法，另一方面则成几何层...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">34有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6556160_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6556160_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










