              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>他的经历了后来一长串行动者思考的行动</q></blockquote>
his action mediated through a chain of subsequent actors<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>疑似把”mediated“看成”meditate“了，否则很难解释为什么会出现”思考“。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







